{"tid":1795132,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"應承我，過左今晚就忘記迷雲小隊［流淚emoji]","createTime":"2019-12-23T15:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T09:51:56.000Z","uid":35341,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"089b130c1b15c72ac299e73ff2c3d6bfaf0f6e52","tid":1795132,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:52:48.000Z","msg":"迷雲從來都係一個信念，而唔係十數個人既代號。呢一班人，可能係曾經同我地擦身而過既路人。之所以係迷雲，係因為佢地有迷雲既決心。<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔會想大家記住佢地被block，甚至被恥笑既一刻，佢地只會想大家記住佢地一往無前既決心，為左雲加而奮不顧身既勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n佢地更加唔會想我地因為佢地被block而失去信心，互相指控。😢"},{"pid":"980e7a9d4cb346e0a710018fb48fe9eaf88f9eb7","tid":1795132,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:54:43.000Z","msg":"如果你認為啲反雲係嫁禍既，請你坐言起行搵證據，用一切方法留住證據，等機會黎，幫手足解block，還手足自由。同時諗下，如果到左一日，真係有手足決定用鍵盤以至殺傷力更大既太陽能鍵盤去保護同路人，你準備好支持佢未。核彈都唔割呢一句，對一啲人黎講只係一句口號，但係對某啲人黎講係勇氣既來源。"},{"pid":"511dda5f293511910ceab94fc3f51b9ddbf3dde1","tid":1795132,"uid":35341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www-irishtimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/www.irishtimes.com/polopoly_fs/1.4081999.1573670442!/image/image.jpg_gen/derivatives/landscape_620/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-irishtimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fwww.irishtimes.com%2Fpolopoly_fs%2F1.4081999.1573670442%21%2Fimage%2Fimage.jpg_gen%2Fderivatives%2Flandscape_620%2Fimage.jpg&h=589e5553&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fab940b554b110716a3825345cb63b83b608af2","tid":1795132,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:58:43.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e045a1a0223f06568c8054319c4319fea95887","tid":1795132,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:08:57.000Z","msg":"樓主近況好嗎"},{"pid":"b21e2ec94c4657bad71b8e19055aeedabb1a82ae","tid":1795132,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid